definitions.definition: Any movement of the feet , especially intricate or complex movement, as in sports or dancing .
examples: The dancer impressed the crowd with his fancy footwork .

definitions.definition: A subgenre of juke / ghetto house and style of street dance that originated in Chicago in the early 1990s.

main_definition: Any movement of the feet , especially intricate or complex movement, as in sports or dancing .
